  "title": "Question : use instant search with google map",
  "body": "Hi,\r\n\r\nI'm using Algolia intantsearch and I think it's amaizing !\r\nNow I'd like to add a goole map to search for items (map and refinment list has to be linked)\r\n\r\nI found this example : https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/examples/tourism/\r\nThis is exactlly what I want\r\n\r\n**But I miss some functionnalities** \r\n- Style the map\r\n- Add pop-up windows on markers\r\n\r\nI've search for 2 hours in the internet and couldn't find any good answer.\r\nIt seams I have to build a custom widget ? How ?\r\nMaybe is there a map plugin compatible with Algolia instantSearch (http://leafletjs.com, https://www.mapbox.com) ?\r\n\r\nMy website is developped with Symfony 3 and Jquery\r\n\r\nMany thanks for your help\r\nOlivia",
